   1. Name Scenarios:
      a. Assert the size of the entered text in all the text boxes.
      b. Assert the special/numeric characters inside the "Name" text boxes.
      c. Assert the email entered during Start-up page is same in registration form.
      d. Check if spaces are counted as characters.
      e. Assert error messages on clearing the data inside text boxes.
   
   2. EmailId scenarios: 
      a. Enter invalid email id and check for error message.
      b. Edit the invalid email and enter valid email and check if error message disappears.
      c. Assert error message on deletion of email.
      d. Check if user is able to edit the email id on registration page.
   
   3. Phone number Scenarios:
      a. Check if user can able to enter only numerics in phone number text fields
      b. Assert error message on deleting the entered phn number.
      c. Assert if error message disappears on entering correct number.
      
   4. Post code scenarios:
      a. Assert that user can enter the valid post code
      b. Check that user is not allowed to enter anything other than format (char-int-char-int-char-int)